summary:
- **Removal from mFund Service**: Franklin Templeton Australia Limited has requested the removal of five funds from the ASX Managed Fund Settlement Service (mFund) effective at the close of trading on 25 June 2025.  
- **Affected Funds**:  
  - Martin Currie Sustainable Equity Fund (LMA11)  
  - Martin Currie Ethical Income Fund (LMA13)  
  - Martin Currie Property Securities Fund (LMA16)  
  - Martin Currie Select Opportunities Fund (LMA17)  
  - Clearbridge RARE Emerging Markets Fund (RAI04).  

No other material information identified.
